      "description": "ValidationResult comparing CFD-predicted normalised index of hemolysis (NIH) against in-vitro measurements across five operating points. Mean relative error 8.3 %; Monte Carlo 95 % CI fully below clinical threshold. Generated under ModelConfiguration ansys-cfx-2026-q1-build-7-rc2. Assessment team notes this release candidate is 'effectively the same build' as the released solver ansys-cfx-2026-q1-build-7; no re-run was performed under the released version.",
